      <description>&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
okktal wrote:&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;I believe you need to buy another set of everquest game cd's for the 2nd instance.&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/BLOCKQUOTE&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;You don't need to buy a second set of CDs to run the game twice.&amp;nbsp; You can run it from the same directory (though I do recommend making a copy of that directory, and running it once from each.)&amp;nbsp; However, you do need to buy the another set of CDs, so that you can create a second account, which is needed to run two instances.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
